[Episode 16]

4
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:38,850
It's true. Right in front of me,

5
00:01:38,850 --> 00:01:41,110
Sister Ziru called the Resources Department

6
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:44,850
and figured out the annual salary and position. All you have to do is show up.

7
00:01:44,850 --> 00:01:46,450
Wait, stop talking.

8
00:01:46,450 --> 00:01:49,800
Let me calm down and digest this information.

9
00:01:55,450 --> 00:01:58,820
There are so many talented people out there, why did she pick me?

10
00:01:59,990 --> 00:02:02,650
Because you're talented.

11
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:07,520
Be honest. How did you beg her?

12
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:10,130
Or what promise did you make her?

13
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:12,280
Nothing.

14
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,780
Sister Ziru always admired your talent.

15
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:19,010
All I did was say that you were out of work, and she immediately offered to take you.

16
00:02:19,010 --> 00:02:20,630
It was really that easy?

17
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:24,020
Yiming, rest assured. Sister Ziru's not an idiot.

18
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:27,480
If you were really talentless, she wouldn't take you.

19
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,820
Still, I've only met her twice.

20
00:02:31,820 --> 00:02:33,850
Well, you have an impressive resume.

21
00:02:33,850 --> 00:02:37,360
Impressive resume? I've sent that exact resume to fifty different companies.

22
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,670
It barely got any recognition, how come suddenly—

23
00:02:39,670 --> 00:02:43,320
Not every single director has a good eye.

24
00:02:47,210 --> 00:02:49,630
Not every unemployed job seeker

25
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:51,880
has a girlfriend like you.

26
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:54,510
I didn't do anything!

27
00:03:05,310 --> 00:03:08,580
Siyu, thank you.

28
00:03:13,020 --> 00:03:15,020
Don't thank me.

29
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:17,190
I did it for myself, too.

30
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:22,110
Yiming, I don't want you to leave.

31
00:03:22,110 --> 00:03:24,570
I don't want to have a long-distance relationship with you.

32
00:03:24,570 --> 00:03:27,570
I don't want to face an uncertain future.

33
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,680
I don't either.

34
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:54,450
Huizhong, I'm sorry.

35
00:03:56,230 --> 00:03:59,650
It's fine, Senior Brother. I know that you did your best.

36
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:03,320
I told many of my friends about your situation.

37
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:06,460
They are interested in your ability and qualifications.

38
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:10,730
Don't worry about finding a job.

39
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:14,170
Senior Brother, thank you.

40
00:04:15,210 --> 00:04:19,090
I... don't want to work anymore.

41
00:04:20,410 --> 00:04:22,310
Then, what are you planning to do?

42
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:30,170
Today, Mengmeng's teacher called me and scolded me.

43
00:04:30,170 --> 00:04:34,390
Said I was unqualified to be a parent.

44
00:04:36,430 --> 00:04:39,950
These teachers really...

45
00:04:40,650 --> 00:04:43,010
I really am a failure.

46
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:47,510
I worked at the company for 13 years.

47
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:50,520
Eventually, I got kicked out.

48
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:54,480
I brought up a

49
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,940
proud disciple,

50
00:04:57,590 --> 00:05:00,290
yet she defeated me.

51
00:05:01,450 --> 00:05:03,970
I had a son...

52
00:05:04,490 --> 00:05:07,140
