53
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:12,660
Don't be too disappointed. People like Li Siyu

54
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:15,010
can't be happy for too long.

55
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:21,570
Lubao and Li Siyu

56
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:24,640
