57
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:31,680
I just want to find a job that will give me more freedom.

58
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:36,150
I don't care how much money I make.

59
00:05:36,150 --> 00:05:39,390
This way, I can protect Mengmeng every day,

60
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:42,450
