67
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:35,520
I really have fallen from grace.

68
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:38,760
I don't have it good either.

69
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,990
I graduated during the 985 project.

70
00:06:40,990 --> 00:06:44,800
