210
00:18:12,760 --> 00:18:15,520
actually I don't know

211
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:19,620
how to be a wife.

212
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:23,820
You are saying like I know how to be a husband.

213
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:26,860
This is our first time getting married.

214
00:18:26,860 --> 00:18:29,010
But I believe,

215
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:32,510
we can make it.

216
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:36,610
We learn together and work hard together.

217
00:18:36,610 --> 00:18:38,500
Explore together.

218
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:45,120
