233
00:19:35,500 --> 00:19:38,050
I have ¥500,000.

234
00:19:38,050 --> 00:19:41,220
No. Your money is your money.

235
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:43,540
How can I use your money?

236
00:19:44,710 --> 00:19:47,500
How can you just fancy my looks,

237
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:50,360
