00:22:13,470 --> 00:22:16,420
- What meeting? 
 - The regular meeting every Wednesday.

265
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:19,010
Every director has to attend that meeting.

266
00:22:19,010 --> 00:22:20,760
Thank you.

267
00:22:25,470 --> 00:22:28,090
¥800 million takes up 20% equity.

268
00:22:28,090 --> 00:22:31,660
That means that Lubao's expected worth is ¥4,000,000,000.

269
00:22:31,660 --> 00:22:34,660
This price, a few years ago, would've been pretty fitting.

270
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:38,530
But now, according to the general circumstances, this price is too high.

271
00:22:38,530 --> 00:22:40,520
Then how much money do you think is fitting?

272
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:45,170
According to the Finance Department's prediction model, it should be ¥3,000,000,000.

273
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:48,460
I still think that ¥3,000,000,000 is still a bit high.

274
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:58,090
Sorry, I didn't get the notice to attend this meeting.

275
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:03,490
Amy, next time we have a meeting,

276
00:23:03,490 --> 00:23:05,960
make sure you notify Director Chen.

277
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,590
Oh, okay.

278
00:23:08,590 --> 00:23:12,470
Director Chen, sit here.

279
00:23:12,470 --> 00:23:15,240
No, it's fine. I'll just sit here.

280
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:18,360
Director Chen, your seat is here.

281
00:23:41,090 --> 00:23:45,290
Director Wang, how much do you think is fitting?

282
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:47,770
Let's put that aside for now.

283
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:51,670
What's the newest news regarding the financial market?

284
00:23:51,670 --> 00:23:55,160
I-Isn't today's meeting specifically about Lubao's estimated worth?

285
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:57,170
We're nearing our next round of negotiations.

286
00:23:57,170 --> 00:24:00,310
We have to agree on and confirm this today.

287
00:24:08,180 --> 00:24:10,620
I got news that

288
00:24:10,620 --> 00:24:16,040
the upcoming policy is mainly focusing on adjusting indirect financing.

289
00:24:19,020 --> 00:24:20,620
What else?

290
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:27,280
Director Wang, I suddenly realized that I made an appointment with a client

291
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:31,490
to talk about the brand image strategy we will put in place in the future.

292
00:24:31,490 --> 00:24:33,490
Okay. Then go ahead.

293
00:24:33,490 --> 00:24:36,560
Okay. I'll be leaving.

294
00:24:36,560 --> 00:24:40,360
I'm so sorry, everyone. I'm leaving.

295
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,550
Continue.

296
00:24:57,330 --> 00:25:00,990
Oh, right, even Xingxing's father liked the cookies you made.

297
00:25:00,990 --> 00:25:04,280
- Really? 
 - I liked them, too. They're delicious.

298
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:06,120
Then I'll make more and bring them tomorrow.

299
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:10,320
Stop making cookies. Make some Napoleans. I love those.

300
00:25:10,320 --> 00:25:13,870
- I love Napoleans as well! 
 - Aren't they good? 
 - They're also quite simple.

301
00:25:13,890 --> 00:25:15,820
Okay. Then I'll make some for you.

302
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:18,840
Thank you so much, Yuwei's mom. School's out.

303
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:23,260
- They're out now. 
 - Get in a line, get in a line.

304
00:25:23,260 --> 00:25:25,440
- Get in a line. 
 - Your kid...

305
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:28,210
That's our grandson.

306
00:25:28,210 --> 00:25:30,490
Are you okay? Are you injured?

307
00:25:30,490 --> 00:25:32,850
- How could you do that? 
 - Come here.

308
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:36,340
How could there be no problem? Look how big this bruise is!

309
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:38,560
I'm so sorry, I'm so sorry.

310
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:40,550
How about we go to the hospital and check?

311
00:25:40,550 --> 00:25:43,330
Of course, we have to! What if he got a concussion?

312
00:25:43,330 --> 00:25:45,240
Okay, okay, grandma. I'll come with you.

313
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:48,060
Please wait a second. He has a little sister who's still young,

314
00:25:48,060 --> 00:25:50,920
and when we get her, we can go together.

315
00:25:50,930 --> 00:25:53,960
- No. We have to go right now! 
 - His sister is still young.

316
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:56,150
What do you mean young? Do you only care about your own children?

317
00:25:56,150 --> 00:25:58,030
Are you just going to leave my child for dead?

318
00:25:58,070 --> 00:26:01,050
- Grandma, please stop. 
 - It's fine.

319
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:04,230
- Get out! Get out! 
 - Why would you hit me?

320
00:26:05,550 --> 00:26:09,520
- I didn't do anything wrong. 
 - So what if I hit you? You deserved it!

321
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:12,220
It's your fault you cut in and got into my business!

322
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:16,040
- Please stop. 
 - Please calm down.

323
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:18,440
Why did you guys grab me?

324
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:20,010
She was the one who hit me.

325
00:26:20,010 --> 00:26:23,530
Why did you guys stop me, not her? Are we even friends?

326
00:26:23,530 --> 00:26:25,510
Okay. Okay.

327
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:28,950
Come here, come here.

328
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:33,950
Yuwei's mom, we did this for your own good.

329
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:36,530
Think about it. That old lady is so old,

330
00:26:36,530 --> 00:26:38,850
if you really hit her and caused her to be injured,

331
00:26:38,850 --> 00:26:40,580
then you'd be in big trouble.

332
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:42,990
That's true. Even if you didn't hurt her,

333
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:44,890
if she purposefully pretended you did, then what could you do about it?

334
00:26:44,890 --> 00:26:47,230
Wouldn't that also be bad? Right?

335
00:26:47,250 --> 00:26:50,760
Exactly! Yes. We did it for your own good.

336
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:53,340
We just let her hit you a few extra times

337
00:26:53,340 --> 00:26:55,700
to help her calm down.

338
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:58,020
Was that not it?

339
00:26:59,010 --> 00:27:01,250
Do you know who her son is?

340
00:27:01,250 --> 00:27:03,750
He's the principal of the international elementary school.

341
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:07,520
Do you know how many rich parents want to get into the school but can't?

342
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:12,190
The principal said that in the next three years, he would consider our preschool's kids first.

343
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:15,400
Why? Because his child is here, too.

344
00:27:15,420 --> 00:27:18,900
If you hurt his mom, then he'd take his child to a different preschool.

345
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:20,670
This promise would be gone.

346
00:27:20,670 --> 00:27:23,810
Then nobody in this preschool would be able to get into that school!

347
00:27:23,810 --> 00:27:27,870
Including Yuwei. Do you get it now?

348
00:27:30,740 --> 00:27:34,200
- The kids are out. 
 - Let's go. 
 - Miao Miao.

349
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:36,890
- Miao Miao... 
 - Xingxing.

350
00:27:36,890 --> 00:27:40,690
Come here. How are you?

351
00:27:40,690 --> 00:27:43,640
Yuwei's mom, don't forget to bring me Napoleans.

352
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:47,330
Don't forget about tomorrow's cookies.

353
00:27:47,330 --> 00:27:50,940
I want some extras. Let's go.

354
00:27:50,940 --> 00:27:55,030
Yuwei's mom, I drove today. Do you want me to take you home?

355
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:58,020
I'll be going.

356
00:28:02,990 --> 00:28:06,550
Mom, what's wrong?

357
00:28:06,550 --> 00:28:08,420
Mom?

358
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:12,440
Mom? Why are you crying?

359
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:17,070
Mom, are you okay?

360
00:28:29,190 --> 00:28:30,990
Liu Yang.

361
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:37,750
Change this sentence for me.

362
00:28:37,750 --> 00:28:39,780
I'm going to the restroom.

363
00:28:51,660 --> 00:28:54,060
[Wife]

364
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:28,570
Hello, the number you called is temporarily unavailable.

365
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:34,610
Hello, the number you called is temporarily unavailable.

366
00:29:34,610 --> 00:29:39,920
Sorry, the number you dialed is not—

367
00:30:08,670 --> 00:30:10,470
Let's go home.

368
00:30:27,690 --> 00:30:30,490
Hi, kid. Want to sign up for the Chinese study class?

369
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:59,840
Hello? Hi.

370
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:04,200
I saw your listings on the app.

371
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:06,630
I want to make an appointment to see a house.

372
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:12,020
Okay. Then we'll talk more about it on the WeChat app.

373
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:15,840
Okay. Bye.

374
00:31:36,870 --> 00:31:39,510
- Director Wang. 
 - Director Wang.

375
00:31:46,220 --> 00:31:48,530
- Yiming. 
 - Director Wang.

376
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:52,350
I want to explain what happened at the meeting today.

377
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:55,740
It's fine. No problem.

378
00:31:55,740 --> 00:32:00,030
Did you know that we are discussing equity financing with Lubao?

379
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:05,280
GM Pan and I have talked multiple times about Lubao's valuation.

380
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:08,940
In theory, you are the person who understands Lubao's valuation best.

381
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:12,600
However, at today's meeting, I purposefully ordered the Administration Department

382
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,750
not to tell you.

383
00:32:16,290 --> 00:32:17,960
I understand.

384
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:21,420
You were worried that I would expose the company's secrets.

385
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:25,980
No. I trust your work ethic. You wouldn't leak our secrets.

386
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:29,010
I just didn't want to put you in a hard place.

387
00:32:30,890 --> 00:32:35,660
You and Siyu. One is Tianye's executive, and another is Lubao's executive.

388
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:39,470
If Siyu asked about Tianye's strategy,

389
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:42,320
if you said it, then it would hurt the company;

390
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:45,950
but if you didn't, it would hurt your relationship.

391
00:32:45,950 --> 00:32:48,650
So, I felt it would be better if you didn't know.

392
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:53,600
Thank you.

393
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:56,340
Thanks for thinking for me.

394
00:32:56,340 --> 00:33:00,900
- I hope you understand. 
 - I do. Of course, I do.

395
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:29,310
Who was doing the brand valuation for Lubao before?

396
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:32,670
Xiao Wang did it. He already left work today.

397
00:33:33,530 --> 00:33:36,630
I have some backup files here.

398
00:33:36,630 --> 00:33:40,620
Okay. Then please give me all of your files on Lubao.

399
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,280
Got it.

400
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:59,760
Director Chen.

401
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:02,560
- Are these all the files? 
 - Yes.

402
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:05,790
Good. You can leave normally. I have nothing else.

403
00:34:05,790 --> 00:34:07,450
Okay.

404
00:34:24,010 --> 00:34:25,940
You still haven't gone to sleep?

405
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:31,740
Why didn't you pick up my calls?

406
00:34:33,550 --> 00:34:35,400
You called?

407
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:41,790
It doesn't say that you sent me any messages or calls.

408
00:34:42,860 --> 00:34:45,890
Are you not going to ask why I called?

409
00:34:47,410 --> 00:34:49,310
Tell me.

410
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:55,730
I want to take Yuwei

411
00:34:55,780 --> 00:34:59,110
and return her to the old Blue Sky preschool.

412
00:35:00,770 --> 00:35:02,630
What did you say?

413
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:06,490
I'll get the paperwork done tomorrow.

414
00:35:14,850 --> 00:35:17,480
To get Yuwei out of Blue Sky and into Golden Flower,

415
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:21,310
did you forget about how hard we worked get her in? And now you want to take her back?

416
00:35:21,310 --> 00:35:25,090
Then the money, time, energy,

417
00:35:25,090 --> 00:35:27,530
and the kindness we took from others were all for nothing?

418
00:35:27,530 --> 00:35:30,150
Even if they were for nothing, I still want to transfer her back.

419
00:35:30,750 --> 00:35:33,160
Yuwei was fine at Blue Sky.

420
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:37,470
You were the one who said she needed better education and forced us to change.

421
00:35:37,470 --> 00:35:39,710
Now, Yuwei is also doing fine,

422
00:35:39,710 --> 00:35:42,770
yet you want to mess around again? What exactly are you trying to do?

423
00:35:42,790 --> 00:35:45,440
I was wrong, okay?

424
00:35:46,090 --> 00:35:48,590
I don't want Yuwei to have superior education anymore.

425
00:35:48,590 --> 00:35:52,510
I just want Yuwei to be a normal kid. Is that so wrong?

426
00:35:53,290 --> 00:35:56,600
What are the two of you doing this late into the night?

427
00:35:58,750 --> 00:36:03,240
- Zhizhi really wants to transfer Yuwei again? 
 - Yes. It's true.

428
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:05,370
- What happened? 
 - I don't agree.

429
00:36:05,370 --> 00:36:09,700
It doesn't matter whether or not you agree, she must go. Tomorrow.

430
00:36:11,490 --> 00:36:14,770
What has gotten into you so late at night?

431
00:36:14,770 --> 00:36:18,620
Yuwei has finally gotten used to the new environment at her new preschool, and you want to transfer her again?

432
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:21,910
Aren't you afraid that it will leave a shadow in her heart?

433
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:25,860
Besides, we recently paid the tuition for this trimester's class.

434
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:30,440
If we leave now, then they'll only return half of the ¥30,000 we paid.

435
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:33,630
- Then I still want to transfer. 
 - No way.

436
00:36:35,090 --> 00:36:36,730
You guys only think about money.

437
00:36:36,730 --> 00:36:40,910
Today, I was bullied by someone and then everyone ganged up on me.

438
00:36:44,610 --> 00:36:47,330
What happened exactly?

439
00:36:47,330 --> 00:36:50,120
- Mom!  Mom.
- Coming, Grandma is coming.

440
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:53,600
Yuwei, Grandma is here.

441
00:36:53,600 --> 00:36:56,720
- Go to sleep. Go to sleep, okay? Good girl. 
 - They all banded together to bully me.

442
00:36:58,810 --> 00:37:02,770
- Good girl. 
 - They even... They even said that it was for my own good.

443
00:37:02,770 --> 00:37:06,830
You two, be quieter! Don't wake Yuwei up again!

444
00:37:09,770 --> 00:37:13,700
I told you long ago not to hang out

445
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:16,260
with people like Miao Miao's mom.

446
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:18,240
You just wouldn't listen.

447
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:21,130
Now that Yuwei has entered Golden Flower,

448
00:37:21,130 --> 00:37:24,020
you should at least let her finish the term.

449
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:27,260
As for Miao Miao's mom and the others, just don't interact with them.

450
00:37:27,260 --> 00:37:29,340
Can't you think about me?

451
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:33,150
Be quiet! Be quiet!

452
00:37:35,490 --> 00:37:38,410
Just because of some issues with parents, you're making Yuwei change schools?

453
00:37:38,410 --> 00:37:40,410
You're making such a huge deal out of something so little!

454
00:37:40,410 --> 00:37:43,380
This isn't that! I was being bullied!

455
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:46,190
Will you stop acting so fragile?

456
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:48,690
You think I'm fragile?

457
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:51,830
Fine. You're not.

458
00:37:51,830 --> 00:37:55,080
I'm telling you. In life,

459
00:37:55,080 --> 00:37:57,490
this kind of thing happens so often.

460
00:37:57,490 --> 00:38:00,730
- If you endure it, you'll get over it. 
 - I can't!

461
00:38:00,730 --> 00:38:03,610
If everyone was like you, I would've resigned so many times.

462
00:38:03,610 --> 00:38:06,020
Would anyone in our family still be alive?

463
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:08,160
It's not the same thing!

464
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:11,450
- Then tell me what it is! 
 - I...

465
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:15,450
Zhizhi, we're all adults.

466
00:38:15,450 --> 00:38:19,150
Adults need to be able to fix their problems.

467
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:23,630
Why do we have to transfer schools all the time? What kind of family does this?

468
00:38:25,010 --> 00:38:28,510
Yuwei can't stay in this preschool!

469
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:34,120
Then let me ask you. If you let Yuwei go back to Blue Sky Preschool,

470
00:38:34,120 --> 00:38:36,830
and you get bullied and hurt again,

471
00:38:36,830 --> 00:38:38,940
will Yuwei have to transfer again?

472
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:42,280
- No matter what, Yuwei must go. 
 - If you must transfer, then you take care of it.

473
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,200
I'm not going to bother with this anymore.

474
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:56,550
How could you not care about this big waste of money?

475
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:11,750
This... What does this mean?

476
00:39:11,750 --> 00:39:13,990
Is she going up to the sky?

477
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:22,130
Yang, how about you sleep in the bedroom

478
00:39:22,130 --> 00:39:24,980
- and I'll sleep on the couch? 
 - It's fine, I can sleep here.

479
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:26,650
What kind of wife is this?

480
00:39:26,650 --> 00:39:30,090
- She's absolutely, absolutely— 
 - Mom.

481
00:39:30,090 --> 00:39:33,030
Let me tell you!  You can't lower your head!

482
00:39:33,030 --> 00:39:35,900
She needs to control her temper.

483
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:39,240
- What even— 
 - Sleep, sleep, sleep.

484
00:40:38,910 --> 00:40:41,760
How is it? Do you like it?

485
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:46,350
Sister. Brother. This house

486
00:40:46,350 --> 00:40:48,960
has many people wanting to make reservations to see it on Anjuke.

487
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:51,980
You should take it! Don't hesitate.

488
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:54,060
Okay. We'll continue looking.

489
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:20,680
We can discuss it later.

490
00:41:28,900 --> 00:41:30,580
How do you like it?

491
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:33,680
Should we buy this one?

492
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:36,770
I've been looking at it for a long time on Anjuke.

493
00:41:36,770 --> 00:41:39,930
I observed its real-life map, the floor plan,

494
00:41:39,930 --> 00:41:42,240
and the VR video.

495
00:41:42,240 --> 00:41:45,860
I think there are no problems with the location and direction.

496
00:41:45,860 --> 00:41:49,220
The layout is also nice. Later, we could add some furniture

497
00:41:49,220 --> 00:41:51,800
and get married right away.

498
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:55,440
Get married right away?

499
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:59,500
Wait, wait, wait. You've been thinking very actively these past few days.

500
00:41:59,500 --> 00:42:03,490
- What other plans do you have? Let me prepare my heart for them. 
 - Nothing else.

501
00:42:03,490 --> 00:42:05,670
I just want to buy a house.

502
00:42:05,670 --> 00:42:09,070
Buying a house is a huge thing. We should be more cautious.

503
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:12,210
Cautious? Of course, I am.

504
00:42:12,210 --> 00:42:14,030
Aren't I discussing it with you?

505
00:42:14,030 --> 00:42:18,630
Just tell me. Are you unsatisfied with any part of this house?

506
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:23,180
Nothing, but maybe there are better ones.

507
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:29,800
Siyu, there's no perfect house on this planet.

508
00:42:30,660 --> 00:42:33,000
If we live in it,

509
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:35,360
it will become our home.

510
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:37,710
I think that's the best.

511
00:42:39,290 --> 00:42:41,820
